description: Caribbean Cafe Truck owners grew up in a home that was always fullof the aromatic scents of delicious Caribbean food. The scents and the flavors were like a paradise of their own. The aromas of their food will certainly make you feel like you're in a CaribbeanParadise!Caribbean Cafe Truck would like everyone to experience the full robustflavor of the Caribbean nations. Their foodtruck is bringing their own savory brand of “deliciousness” to the palates of Washington DC. We know you will enjoy our cuisine as much as we doand as much as we enjoy preparing it for you.
name: Caribbean Cafe Truck
